    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Medical Appointment No-Show Prediction\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Project 32 of 100 — Classification Portfolio**\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Project Overview\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"This project predicts whether a patient will miss their scheduled medical appointment (no-show). We build a full classification pipeline using **LazyPredict** for benchmarking, **FLAML** for AutoML, and evaluate the **top 3 models** with proper metrics.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Missed appointments cost healthcare systems billions annually in wasted resources. Predicting no-shows allows clinics to implement overbooking strategies and targeted reminders.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"1. Handle class imbalance in a real-world healthcare classification problem\\n\",\n",
    "    \"2. Engineer temporal features from appointment and scheduling dates\\n\",\n",
    "    \"3. Use LazyPredict and FLAML to find the best model families\\n\",\n",
    "    \"4. Evaluate with imbalance-aware metrics (F1, PR-AUC)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"5. Interpret results for actionable healthcare recommendations\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Problem Statement\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Given patient demographics, appointment details, and health conditions, predict whether a patient will show up for their appointment or not.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"This is a **binary classification** problem: `No-show = Yes` (missed) vs `No-show = No` (showed up).\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Why This Project Matters\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Healthcare efficiency**: ~20-30% of appointments are missed, wasting clinician time and resources\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Patient outcomes**: Missed appointments delay treatment and worsen health outcomes\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Operational planning**: Prediction enables proactive scheduling and reminder systems\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **ML skills**: Teaches handling of class imbalance, date feature engineering, and healthcare domain thinking\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Dataset Overview\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Property | Value |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"|----------|-------|\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| **Source** | Kaggle — `joniarroba/noshowappointments` |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| **Records** | ~110,000 |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| **Features** | 14 |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| **Target** | `No-show` (Yes/No) |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| **Task** | Binary classification |\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Dataset Source and License Notes\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Platform**: Kaggle (https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/joniarroba/noshowappointments)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **License**: CC BY-NC-SA 4.0\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Original source**: Brazilian public healthcare system\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Download**: Via `kagglehub` or `opendatasets`\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Environment Setup\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
